comments.body: Oh, this is already happening. Maybe it's call slip configuration? @kevinreiss can you take a look and make sure ItemInfo4 is rendering on call slips?

Can you see the value in the ItemInfo4 field in the request Aeon recorded? If you can and it's not printing out than it's an issue with the print template itself. If it's not there and Aeon isn't accepting the value pulfalight is passing that's weirder and needs to be a support ticket to atlas. If you need help with the print templates also please put in a support ticket with Atlas.
